# Auto-load the Nix dev shell (flake.nix) on `cd` into this directory.
# Requires direnv + nix-direnv. Run `direnv allow` once to enable.
# This is the Nix-world equivalent of a dotenv file: it provides the
# environment (cc, python3, the elan-managed Lean toolchain) for both your
# terminal and, via the direnv VSCode extension, the Lean 4 language server.
use flake
